elements.name: As a user i want to check that i have access to Hotel Management Platform application with invalid credentials

steps.name: I navigate to the "Hotel Management Platform" application in browser
I want to see the application is loaded in browser by verifying the essential elements on the page
I click on Login link in the Menu bar
I should see the login dialogue box with Username and password
With out providing the credentials When I click the Login button in Login dialogue
I can't enter into the management platform
I enter invalid "username" and "password" in the respective textfields and click login button
I should not enter into the application
